article_title: Closer Look At Path Of Wessington Springs Tornado
article_text:
Wessington Springs, SD

The South Dakota Highway Patrol shares a unique view of the damage in Wessington Springs.

Video from the agency follows the EF-2 tornado's path into the central South Dakota town. The line of debris comes from damage at dozens of homes and businesses.

The twister that hit town created a two mile long path that was 30 yards wide.
